data.description: ** $5000 BUYER INCENTIVE ** We are proud to present this exquisite new listing in Sendera Ranch! Nestled in a court with a greenbelt, this home is a one of a kind. The immaculate condition is evident from the moment you walk in the door with the laminate wood floors, open concept living, granite counters, and white kitchen cabinets. With 4 bedrooms and an upstairs flex space, this house has the space you need to stretch out your legs. When enjoying your coffee on the back patio, there is just a view of green pastures to enjoy with the peace and serenity you crave. To make this one even more impeccable, the home is located in Northwest ISD with a school just down the street for ease of drop off and pick up! This warm and inviting home is exactly what you have been looking for! Do not delay and schedule a showing today!
